	</div>
	<div class="commentBody">
		<div id="comment_body_64499061">There are four options, really:<br> <br>

- Plenty and equality: Star Trek future goes here.<br>
- Plenty and inequality: All the replicators have DRM and intellectual property is everything.<br>
- Scarcity and equality: If the AIs are too expensive for everybody to use, but we ration its use sanely.<br>
- Scarcity and hierarchy: The owners hoard the supercomputers and let everybody else enjoy a working poor life.</div>
	</div>

